    "13413542": {
      "title": "Mega2: data-handling for facilitating genetic linkage and association analyses",
      "abstract": "Summary: Mega2, the manipulation environment for genetic analysis, transparently allows users to process genetic data for family-based or case/control studies accurately and efficiently. In addition to data validation checks, Mega2 provides analysis setup capabilities for a broad choice of commonly used genetic analysis programs, including SimWalk2, ASPEX, GeneHunter, SLINK, SIMULATE, S.A.G.E., SOLAR, Vitesse, Allegro, PREST, PAP, Loki, Merlin and MENDEL. ::: ::: Availability: http://watson.hgen.pitt.edu/register/ ::: ::: Contact: dweeks@watson.hgen.pitt.edu ::: ::: Supplementary information: http://watson.hgen.pitt.edu/docs/mega2_html/mega2.html"
    }
  },
